【Professor Scorlan】 There are two types of magic.
One is the magic that imitates and studies the
magic of demons.

【Professor Scorlan】 It is something created by
humanity.

【Professor Scorlan】 Magic that imitates demons
tends to be more focused on offensive spells,
while magic created by humans tends to be more
useful.

【Professor Scorlan】 For example, illumination
magic is one such magic.

【Professor Scorlan】 This is also due to the
Samuel Church restricting the study of magic.

【Masamune】 Hey, I wonder who the strongest
magician in this academy is.
スキット 表情 レオン f 1
スキット スライドイン レオン f 左

【Leon】 That's a question that's close to being
taboo.
【Masamune】 Is that so?
スキット 表情 レオン f 3

【Leon】 The second faction in Caledonia is the
Student Council and the Magic Research Club.
スキット 表情 レオン f 7

【Leon】 The representatives are Vice President
Olivia and President Jackson. Every day, fans
debate who is stronger.
スキット 表情 レオン f 6

【Leon】 However, no conclusive results are reached
and it often leads to arguments.
【Masamune】 Oh... I see...

【Skeleton Head】 However, I can't help but wonder
which one of them is stronger.

【Masamune】 Skeleton Head, who do you think is
stronger?
スキット 表情 レオン f 3

【Skeleton Head】 Of course, it's Vice President
Olivia. She can use a special class magic called
Planetary Magic.

【Skeleton Head】 However, according to rumors, her
best magic is Puppet Manipulation Magic.

【Masamune】 Are you better at magic other than
advanced class magic? By the way, what kind of
magic is it?

【Skeleton Head】 It seems that she uses Puppet
Manipulation Magic to control dolls and
automatically handle security in the Student
Council room.
【Masamune】 That's amazing.

【Masamune】 Then it's definitely Vice President
Olivia who takes the top spot.

【Tommy】 Well, it's not like that. There are
rumors about the Vice President too, saying that
her magic power has weakened compared to the
second year students.

【Tommy】 So, I think Jackson-senpai is stronger
now.

【Masamune】 Weak... But there's no way she would
weaken at this age.

【Tommy】 Yeah, but it's actually true. And there
are also rumors that no one has ever seen her
eating recently.

【Masamune】 Is she not feeling well... But Tommy
seems to be a fan of Jackson-senpai.

【Tommy】 No, I'm also on the Vice President's
side.
【Skeleton Head】 She's cute, isn't she?
【Tommy】 Y-Yeah...
スキット 表情 レオン f 2

【Leon】 By the way, I'm also on Vice President
Olivia's side.

【Masamune】 Everyone seems to be on the Vice
President's side, huh?
スキット 終了
